---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const updated = "October 3, 2025";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service | Knit by Machine" description="Terms of service for Knit by Machine - eligibility, use of services, memberships, and intellectual property.">
  <style>
    :root {
      --kbm-green: #52682d;
      --kbm-green-2: #738c52;
      --page-bg: #f7f8f7;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 860px;
      padding: 80px 20px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .kbm-breadcrumb {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .kbm-legal h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    }

    .meta {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .kbm-card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 24px 22px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }

    .kbm-toc {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      margin: 0 0 24px 0;
    }

    .kbm-toc details summary {
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .kbm-toc nav a {
      display: block;
      padding: 6px 0;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--kbm-green);
    }

    .kbm-toc nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Back-to-top button */
    #kbm-top {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 30px;
      right: 30px;
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--kbm-green);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      z-index: 9999;
    }

    #kbm-top.show {
      opacity: 1;
      visibility: visible;
    }

    #kbm-top:hover {
      background: var(--kbm-green-2);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
  </style>

  <main>
    <div class="kbm-legal">
      <div class="kbm-breadcrumb">Knit by Machine ▸ Terms of Service</div>
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <div class="meta">Last updated: {updated}</div>

      <aside class="kbm-toc">
        <details open>
          <summary>On this page</summary>
          <nav>
            <a href="#eligibility">1. Eligibility</a>
            <a href="#use-of-services">2. Use of Services</a>
            <a href="#accounts">3. Accounts</a>
            <a href="#payments">4. Memberships, Purchases, and Payments</a>
            <a href="#ip">5. Intellectual Property</a>
            <a href="#user-content">6. User Content</a>
            <a href="#warranty">7. Disclaimer of Warranties</a>
            <a href="#liability">8. Limitation of Liability</a>
            <a href="#changes">9. Changes to These Terms</a>
            <a href="#termination">10. Termination</a>
            <a href="#law">11. Governing Law</a>
            <a href="#contact">12. Contact Us</a>
          </nav>
        </details>
      </aside>

      <section class="kbm-card">
        <h2 id="eligibility">1. Eligibility</h2>
        <p>You must be at least 18 years old (or the age of majority in your jurisdiction) to use our Services. By using our site, you confirm that you meet this requirement.</p>

        <h2 id="use-of-services">2. Use of Services</h2>
        <p>You may use our Services for personal, non-commercial purposes only, unless we give written permission otherwise. You agree not to misuse our Services, including attempting to interfere with their operation, accessing them using automated means, or using them in a way that violates any laws.</p>

        <h2 id="accounts">3. Accounts</h2>
        <p>Some Services may require creating an account. You are responsible for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Keeping your login details secure</li>
          <li>All activities that occur under your account</li>
          <li>Not sharing your account with others without our permission</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We may suspend or terminate accounts that violate these Terms.</p>

        <h2 id="payments">4. Memberships, Purchases, and Payments</h2>
        <p>If you purchase a membership, course, pattern, or other digital product:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>All prices are shown in USD and subject to change</li>
          <li>Payments are processed through secure third-party providers</li>
          <li>Memberships are billed according to the plan you choose</li>
          <li>Refunds are subject to our Refund Policy</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="ip">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content on our site—including patterns, videos, images, text, and tools—is owned by us or our licensors and is protected by copyright and other laws. Limited personal use is permitted for your own knitting and learning. You may not copy, redistribute, or create derivative works without our written consent.</p>

        <h2 id="user-content">6. User Content</h2>
        <p>If you submit comments, project photos, or other content:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You retain ownership of your content</li>
          <li>You grant us a non-exclusive, royalty-free license to display and share your content in connection with the Services</li>
          <li>You agree not to submit anything unlawful, harmful, or infringing</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="warranty">7. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
        <p>Our Services are provided "as is" and "as available." We do not guarantee that the Services will be error-free, uninterrupted, or suitable for every purpose. Use is at your own risk.</p>

        <h2 id="liability">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>To the fullest extent allowed by law, we are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages resulting from your use of the Services.</p>

        <h2 id="changes">9. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. The "Effective Date" above will reflect the latest version. Continued use of our Services after changes means you accept the updated Terms.</p>

        <h2 id="termination">10. Termination</h2>
        <p>We may suspend or terminate your access to the Services at any time, without notice, if we believe you have violated these Terms.</p>

        <h2 id="law">11. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of California, United States, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>

        <h2 id="contact">12. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about these Terms, please contact us at:</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:contact@KnitbyMachine.com">contact@KnitbyMachine.com</a></p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <button id="kbm-top" aria-label="Back to top">↑</button>
  </main>

  <script>
    const topBtn = document.getElementById("kbm-top");
    if (topBtn) {
      window.addEventListener("scroll", () => {
        if (window.scrollY > 200) {
          topBtn.classList.add("show");
        } else {
          topBtn.classList.remove("show");
        }
      });

      topBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
        window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: "smooth" });
      });
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
